metadata.name: Casco Viejo
metadata.description:
"Casco Viejo" is a piece inspired by one of the most emblematic historical and tourist centers of Panama City. The so-called ancient city. My first encounter with her was in 2016 and since then she has been my favorite place in the whole city.

Photography + Code + Glitch process
2828x4242 px
PNG

by Daniel Oropeza
